      • saveInBackground

        public static void saveInBackground(MLObject object,
                    SaveCallback callback,
                    FileProgressCallback fileProgressCallback)
        Saves the object to the server in a background thread.if contains MLFile,you can set a FileProgressCallback to listens the file upload progress.
        参数:
        object - the object
        callback - callback.done(e) is called when the save completes.
        fileProgressCallback - fileProgressCallback.done() is call when contains MLFile.

        public static <T extends MLObject> void deleteAllInBackground(List<T> objects)

        类型参数:
        T -
        参数:
        objects - The objects to delete.
